    <sentence>
      <text>Ow!</text>
      <textCn>啊哟!</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>What's the matter, Andy?</text>
      <textCn>怎么了，安迪？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I slipped and fell downstairs.</text>
      <textCn>我滑了一跤，从楼梯上摔下来了。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Have you hurt yourself?</text>
      <textCn>你摔伤了没有？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Yes, I have.</text>
      <textCn>是啊，摔伤了。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I think that I've hurt my back.</text>
      <textCn>我想我把背摔坏了。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Try and stand up.</text>
      <textCn>试试站起来。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Can you stand up?</text>
      <textCn>你能站起来吗？</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>Here. Let me help you.</text>
      <textCn>来，让我帮你。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I'm sorry, Lucy.</text>
      <textCn>对不起，露西。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I'm afraid that I can't get up.</text>
      <textCn>恐怕我站不起来。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I think that the doctor had better see you.</text>
      <textCn>我想最好请医生来看一下。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I'll phone Dr. Carter.</text>
      <textCn>我去给卡特医生打电话。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>The doctor says that he will come at once.</text>
      <textCn>医生说他马上就来。</textCn>
    </sentence>
    <sentence>
      <text>I'm sure that you need an X-ray, Andy.</text>
      <textCn>安迪，我看你需要做一次 X 光透视。</textCn>
